More IQA Atomic Energy Components:
---------------------------------
  Vneen(A) = Vne(A,Mol)/2 + Ven(A,Mol)/2
  V_IQA(A) = Vne(A,Mol)/2 + Ven(A,Mol)/2 + Vee(A,A) + Vee(A,A')/2 + Vnn(A,A')/2
           = VC_IQA(A) + VX_IQA(A) = Potential Energy Contribution to E_IQA(A)
           = E_IQA(A) - T(A)
  VC_IQA(A) = Vne(A,Mol)/2 + Ven(A,Mol)/2 + VeeC(A,A) + VeeC(A,A')/2 + Vnn(A,A')/2
            = Coulomb Potential Energy Contribution to E_IQA(A)
            = E_IQA(A) - T(A) - VeeX(A)
  VX_IQA(A) = VeeX(A,A) + VeeX(A,A')/2
            = Exchange-Correlation Energy Contribution to E_IQA(A)
            = E_IQA(A) - T(A) - VC_IQA(A)
See "2EDM Note" and "DFT Note".
