Atomic Radial Distortion Moments:
--------------------------------
  Dot = x*(dRho/dx) + y*(dRho/dy) + z*(dRho/dz)
  GR-2(A) = <Dot/(r*r)>(A)
  GR-1(A) = <Dot/r>(A)
  GR0(A)  = <Dot>(A)
  GR+1(A) = <Dot*r>(A)
  GR+2(A) = <Dot*r*r>(A)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
